Source: libquvi
Section: libs
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Alejandro Garrido Mota <garridomota@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), libcurl4-dev, libpcre3-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.4
Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/quvi

Package: libquvi0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: library for parsing video download links runtime libraries
 The library is written in C and lets to parse video download links.
 It supports Youtube and other similar video websites

Package: libquvi-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, (= ${binary:Version})
Description: library for parsing video download links development package
 The library is written in C and lets to parse video download links.
 It supports Youtube and other similar video websites
 .
 This package provides the files necessary to compile programs which
 use libquvi0

Package: libquvi-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: library for parsing video download links development package
 The library is written in C and lets to parse video download links.
 It supports Youtube and other similar video websites
 .
 This package provides the documentation necessary to use the library

Package: quvi
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: command line tool for parsing video download links
 command line tool written in C for parsing video download links.
 It supports Youtube and other similar video websites
